data.description: Discover modern elegance in this remodeled 3-bed, 2-bath home on a 3/4-acre lot. Step into a living area with fresh paint and gleaming floors. The chef's kitchen boasts new appliances. The serene master suite features an updated bath and ample closets. Two more bedrooms offer flexibility.  Conveniently located in the country but close to town. Seller's are also including $5,000 towards closing cost or purchases of new appliances or mini splits for home.
